date.textblock: The closed meeting scheduled for Wednesday, February 23, 1994 at 4:00 p.m., was changed to Wednesday, February 23, 1994 at 11:30 a.m.
Commissioner Beese, as duty officer, determined that Commission business required the above change and that no earlier notice thereof was possible.

At times, changes in Commission priorities require alterations in the scheduling of meeting items. For further information and to ascertain what, if any, matters have been added, deleted or postponed, please contact: John Ramsey at (202) 272-2100.
